    v1 = (wp.exp(0.00) / ((v0 + 0.13 - tmp + 0.80) + wp.abs(v1 + 0.36)))
    v2 = (wp.exp(tmp) + 0.27)
    v1 = (wp.sin(tmp) * (tmp - (v2 + 0.88 / v2 + 0.67)))
    tmp = v1
